T* (Abstract) Tj
T* (Choosing secondary indexes is a classic trade-off between read acceleration and write) Tj
T* (amplification.) Tj
T* (We benchmark eight index configurations across OLTP and HTAP-style workloads and report when) Tj
T* (composite indexes stop paying off.) Tj
